managerNotification.body:
Hi {{managerFirstName}},

This is a confirmation that {{firstName}} {{lastName}} is scheduled to start as {{title}} on {{startDate}}.

**New Hire Details:**
- Name: {{firstName}} {{lastName}}
- Position: {{title}}
- Department: {{department}}
- Start Date: {{startDate}}
- Email: {{email}}

**IT Setup Status:**
- Workstation: {{workstationStatus}}
- Accounts: {{accountStatus}}
- Equipment: {{equipmentStatus}}

**Action Items for You:**
- Schedule first-day orientation meeting
- Prepare workspace and introduce to team
- Review first week training schedule
- Assign initial projects/tasks

The IT department has created the onboarding ticket #{{ticketNumber}} to track all setup tasks. You can view the progress in Autotask.

If you need any additional setup or have special requirements, please reply to this email or contact IT at {{itEmail}}.

Best regards,
IT Automation System

